        <h2 id="faq">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <div class="faq-list">
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What is Mangools?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Mangools is a 5-tool SEO suite — KWFinder, SERPChecker, SERPWatcher, LinkMiner, and SiteProfiler — built for beginners, bloggers, and small agencies. Started as KWFinder in 2014 by Peter Hrbáčik in Bratislava, the suite launched in 2016 and now serves 1.1M+ users in 160+ countries.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">How much does Mangools cost in 2026?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Entry $29/mo (annual), Basic $49/mo, Premium $99/mo, Agency $199/mo. 10-day free trial. Annual billing saves 35%. All plans include all 5 tools.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Is Mangools good for beginners?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes — it is the cleanest, most beginner-friendly SEO suite on the market. KWFinder makes low-competition keyword research genuinely simple, and the interface avoids the feature bloat of Semrush and Ahrefs.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Mangools vs Ahrefs — which is better?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Ahrefs has a much larger backlink index, deeper SERP data, and serious features for professionals. Mangools is 1/3 the price, much easier to learn, and covers the basics 90% of small operators need. Pick Mangools for budget + simplicity; Ahrefs for professional-grade depth.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Does Mangools write content?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>No. Mangools is a research-only suite. It finds keywords, tracks rankings, and analyses competitors — but does not write, edit, or publish anything. You still need writers and a publishing workflow.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What does the KWFinder tool do?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>KWFinder is the headline tool. It surfaces low-competition keywords by combining search volume, difficulty score, CPC, trend, and SERP analysis in one clean interface. The KD score is widely regarded as more accurate for low-competition niches than Ahrefs' KD.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">Is there a free trial?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>Yes — 10-day free trial with full access to all 5 tools, no credit card required up front in some markets. The free trial is enough to test the full workflow on a real site.</p></div></div></div>
          <div class="faq-item"><button class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)"><span class="faq-q-text">What is the best Mangools alternative?</span><span class="faq-toggle"><svg viewBox="0 0 12 12"><path d="M6 1v10M1 6h10" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/></svg></span></button><div class="faq-a"><div class="faq-a-inner"><p>For an even cheaper keyword tool: Ubersuggest ($29/mo). For a full SEO suite at higher quality: Ahrefs Lite ($129/mo) or Semrush ($139/mo). For done-for-you content publishing: theStacc ($99/mo).</p></div></div></div>
